response.original_title: DDT New Year☆Dramatic Parade 2026 ~Answer will be given in a year~
response.overview: New Year☆Dramatic Parade 2026 ~Answer will be given in a year~ was a professional wrestling event promoted by Dramatic Dream Team (DDT) that took place on January 3, 2026, at Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, Japan, and was headlined by Yuki Ueno, To-y & Kaisei Takechi (c) vs. MAO, KANON & Kazuma Sumi (with KIMIHIRO) for the KO-D 6-Man Tag Team Championship.
